title: HBE looking for top and support players.

embed.description: Habib eSports Trials (HBE) announces trials for our new and upcoming team. Habib eSports is aiming high with equal expectations, focusing on becoming a frontline in the Oceanic region. This is the beginning of a long commitment and successful players will demonstrate commitment, synergy, sportsmanship, teamwork and the willingness to improve and practice.

body:
HBE are now looking for a support, mid and top laners to begin trials. Applications for ADC and Jungle are closed for the time being as the current applicants are in trials. 

PM 

HBE Hamko
HBE AzzMaster7
